description:
***This is a business application intended for existing Autoniq subscribers only.***

Designed for the iPhones 3GS+ and iPods/iPads with autofocus camera, the Autoniq VIN Barcode Scanner quickly and effectively enhances your existing Autoniq service by reading the VIN barcode on a vehicle using the iPhone or iPad camera.  

This intuitive, easy to use application takes advantage of the iPhone and iPad’s superior technology by providing: 

• state of the art barcode recognition; 
• automatic recognition of normal and square (2D) VIN barcodes;
• automatic focus and exposure adjustment;
• a special keyboard for quick and easy manual VIN entry; 
• an on-screen viewfinder to assist with aiming and VIN barcode placement;
• a copy of the scanned VIN for pasting into other applications; 
• support for camera flash; 

Automobile dealers can now instantly value a vehicle and receive a vehicle history report while making a purchase decision at the auction or on the lot.
